{"tid":1682701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【差佬四點記者會】記者拒絕採訪，是不讓假真相流竄。","createTime":"2019-10-30T08:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T12:04:57.000Z","uid":202464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"584ca6f4e8383576bbc5006272157aa2275679b3","tid":1682701,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"記招係要呼應市民的知情權。<br />\n<br />\n媒體不止報導警察所說的，也要問大眾要知的。<br />\n<br />\n如果記者不能發問，或警方拒絕回答，報道就變了單向資訊。<br />\n<br />\n差佬的居心，就係「講完想講的，不答要答的」。然後媒體報導警察口講的單向資訊，從而引導輿論。<br />\n<br />\n差佬話：「個場係佢哋嘅。」到底呢班人，當不當自己係公僕？"},{"pid":"5d36cb431bd596d5a12e8ffaccbd338eb65c2014","tid":1682701,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b314ae1be1c366029b5de7bffc724c1744610c58","tid":1682701,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d4f51d77931597f931dad48acd9a18cdcbf17f","tid":1682701,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72d0b182629a78d23cd10de5e08acf506050498","tid":1682701,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f4235d5aa05dada89784edbd0b1ad6faea90ce","tid":1682701,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e467740b8f392bb8cebcb52a993ba35be5dfc10","tid":1682701,"uid":287247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:01:27.0